## Quick Reference Guide

### Common Slash Commands Summary

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| `/remind me to [task] [when]` | Set a personal reminder |
| `/remind @person [task] [when]` | Set a reminder for someone else |
| `/dnd [time]` | Enable Do Not Disturb |
| `/status [message]` | Update your status |
| `/msg @person [message]` | Send a direct message from anywhere |
| `/mute` | Mute the current channel |
| `/leave` | Leave the current channel |
| `/collapse` | Hide all images/videos in channel |
| `/expand` | Show all images/videos in channel |
| `/remind list` | See all your reminders |

### Essential Keyboard Shortcuts Summary

| Shortcut (Mac) | Shortcut (Windows) | Action |
|----------------|-------------------|--------|
| Cmd + K | Ctrl + K | Quick Switcher |
| Cmd + / | Ctrl + / | See all shortcuts |
| Cmd + F | Ctrl + F | Search in channel |
| Option + ↑/↓ | Alt + ↑/↓ | Navigate channels |
| Cmd + Shift + A | Ctrl + Shift + A | All Unreads |
| ↑ | ↑ | Edit last message |
| Esc | Esc | Mark channel read |
| Shift + Esc | Shift + Esc | Mark all read |

